Alex shakes her head.
Conrad: Because their methods, however well-intentioned, crossed ethical lines.
Conrad: They manipulated students without consent. They caused harm while trying to teach.
Conrad: You found their methods and repeated their mistakes.
Alex's eyes begin to fill with tears.
Alex: I just... I wanted to help. I wanted to matter, to make a difference like you do.
